# README_CODE

Tai lieu nay mo ta luong hoat dong sau khi da ghep API that cho `dashboard`, `attendance`, `task`.

## 1) Tong quan luong frontend -> backend

1. Dang nhap thanh cong qua `/api/login`, token duoc luu trong localStorage (`messapp_auth_token`).
2. `httpClient` tu dong gan header `Authorization: Bearer <token>` cho tat ca request API.
3. `AuthContext` goi `/api/me` de lay profile (bao gom `role`) va cap nhat UI theo role.
4. Cac page moi su dung API module rieng trong `resources/js/api/*`:
   - `tasksApi.js`
   - `attendanceApi.js`
   - `employeesApi.js`
   - `departmentsApi.js`
5. Error API duoc chuan hoa qua `toApiError` de hien thi thong bao gon.

## 2) Luong trang Task (`/tasks`)

File chinh: `resources/views/task/index.jsx`

- Lay data that tu `GET /api/tasks` (co search `q`, phan trang `per_page`).
- Board chia theo status that: `todo`, `in_progress`, `done`, `cancelled`.
- Tao task: `POST /api/tasks`.
- Chuyen trang thai task: `PUT /api/tasks/{id}`.
- Xoa task: `DELETE /api/tasks/{id}`.
- Role rule backend duoc ton trong:
  - `super_admin/hr_admin/manager`: thay duoc nhieu task theo quyen.
  - `employee`: chi thay task lien quan den minh.

## 3) Luong trang Attendance (`/attendance`)

File chinh: `resources/views/attendance/index.jsx`

- Neu role la `super_admin/hr_admin/manager`:
  - Lay log team: `GET /api/attendance/logs/team`.
  - Lay report: `GET /api/attendance/reports`.
  - Lay department: `GET /api/departments`.
  - Lay employee map: `GET /api/employees` (de ho tro loc theo department).
- Neu role la `employee`:
  - Lay log cua toi: `GET /api/attendance/logs/me`.
- Nut `Manual Clock-in/out`:
  1. Goi `GET /api/attendance/assignments/me` theo ngay dang chon.
  2. Neu co ca dang mo -> `POST /api/attendance/check-out`.
  3. Neu chua check-in -> `POST /api/attendance/check-in`.
- Bang du lieu hien thi gio vao/ra, tong gio, trang thai (`on_time`, `late`, `checked_in`, `absent`) tu data that.

## 4) Luong trang Dashboard (`/dashboard`)

File chinh: `resources/views/dashboard/index.jsx`

- Neu role la `super_admin/hr_admin/manager`:
  - KPI nhan su: `GET /api/employees` (+ filter `employment_status=leave`).
  - KPI task theo trang thai: `GET /api/tasks?status=...`.
  - Du lieu task gan day: `GET /api/tasks`.
  - Attendance health theo thang: `GET /api/attendance/reports`.
- Neu role la `employee`:
  - KPI ca nhan dua tren `GET /api/tasks` (backend tu gioi han theo user).
  - Attendance health ca nhan dua tren `GET /api/attendance/logs/me`.

## 5) Cac file da duoc cap nhat

- API modules:
  - `resources/js/api/tasksApi.js`
  - `resources/js/api/attendanceApi.js`
  - `resources/js/api/employeesApi.js`
  - `resources/js/api/departmentsApi.js`
- Page UI dung data that:
  - `resources/views/task/index.jsx`
  - `resources/views/attendance/index.jsx`
  - `resources/views/dashboard/index.jsx`

## 6) Lam sao de co role `super_admin`

Mac dinh dang ky moi se la `employee` (xem `app/Services/AuthService.php`).

### Cach nhanh nhat (khuyen nghi dev local): dung Tinker

```bash
php artisan tinker
```

```php
$u = App\Models\User::where('phone', '')->first();
$u->role = 'super_admin';
$u->save();
```

Sau do dang xuat va dang nhap lai de refresh profile/role tren frontend.

### Cach SQL truc tiep

```sql
UPDATE users
SET role = 'super_admin'
WHERE email = 'your_email@example.com';
```

## 7) Luu y khi chay local

- Neu `:8000` tra ve `uvicorn`/FastAPI thi Laravel co the dang chay o cong khac (vi du `:8001`).
- Can truy cap dung cong Laravel de xem cac trang dashboard/attendance/task.
